Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.91,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I totally lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.88,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.00,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:19.26,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I gave that performance my all.\N I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.42,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,The loneliness and rage of the Phantom \Nhiding deep within the opera house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:29.14,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I thought expressing that was the key to \Nshowing the Phantom's fear and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.50,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,The variations of the \NPhantom we tried to play
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:36.58,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,are probably extensions\Nof Hiiragi{**-san}'s Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:43.09,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm sure that she saw new \Npotential in Kokona{**-san}.
